item.title: Help me plz!
item.dc:creator: @Sephiroth1 Sephiroth~
item.description:
@Sephiroth1 wrote:

you extract it…

HOW TO EXTRACT FOR DUMBASSES:

  1. Install winRar
  2. right click on pimpscape source
  3. go to the thing that looks like a stack of books
  4. click extract here

Then it should make a new folder

Then you can edit pimpscape by the JAVA files, not the class files, once you finish editing it, you MUST compile it, to run pimpscape click on run.bat (NOTE: i assume you have set ur compiler’s path)
